  "response": "Several US credit cards charge no foreign transaction fees. Here are a few popular options:\n\n1. Chase Sapphire Preferred\u00ae Card\n2. Chase Sapphire Reserve\u00ae\n3. Capital One Venture Rewards Credit Card\n4. Capital One Quicksilver Cash Rewards Credit Card\n5. Discover it\u00ae Cash Back\n6. American Express Gold Card\n7. Bank of America\u00ae Travel Rewards credit card\n\nThese cards are often recommended for travelers due to their lack of foreign transaction fees, which can save you money when making purchases abroad. It's important to check the specific benefits and terms of each card to see which one best suits your needs.",
